\b\pn, it's so good to see you!
\bSo, you remember when I called you a while back, about the fighting Pokemon?
\bWe now have conclusive evidence that that was Delta Regirock! A Delta version of a legendary Pokemon! How wonderful!
\bAnd , more importantly, we now have evidence that Delta Registeel will be passing through the Holon Volcano area!
\bI've already set up a trap for it!
\bI can't wait! This will be my big break!
\b"We'll take away your tenure", they said... oh, I'll show them!
\bI'll make the whole world pay! The world will see the power of my Delta Species Pokemon!
\bBwahahaha! The strongest type of Pokemon of all!
\bSoon, the very university and the entire universe will be stomped afoot!
\b...anyways, yeah, come to the base of the volcano as soon as you can.
\bDelta Registeel should be swinging by soon, and you don't want to be tardy and miss it!
\bIt really sucks that we're not allowed to explore to the top of mountain.
\bThey've closed that off ever since... uh...
\bRemember when the Augur was revealed to be a traitor?
\bIt was around then, if I had to guess.
\bYou know that lightningrod on the mountain?
\bI've been puzzling over it. I know that a lightningrod draws in electricity near it... but I couldn't seem to use an Electric-type move on it directly.
\rI really hope you find a use for it!
\rI really hope you find a use for it!
\bIs nobody else freaked out by the fact that we're, as of right now, standing on top of an active volcano?
\bIt could erupt! What are people thinking?!
\rIt's freezing out, but I'm determined to get my research done.
\rYou gotta stay working hard! Discipline is so important!
An icy force seems to be radiating from this rock.

\bHmph. Look at these boring people, running around and trying to do all these things in the name of science.
\bScience is cool and all but I'd rather not have to be around all these people who go around acting like they've got a stick up their butt all day, y'know?
\bListen, you look different from the rest of the people in this settlement so I figure you'll be able to help me out with my plans.\nMy mission for you is to bring me
\r100 Snowballs \bso that I can stand up here and peg anyone who looks like they're trying too hard to control everything that's going on here.
\bScience is meant to be fun, y'know?
\bAnyways, I'll be waiting for good news from you.
\bOkay, honestly I was just messing with you and wasn't expecting you to get that many.\nI'll take 50 off of your hands and you can keep the rest.
\bHere, you can have these for all your troubles.
\bHmph. Looks like you don't have the 100 Snowballs yet. Don't bother talking to me until you do.
\bFufufu... Finally I can enjoy myself around here.
